summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed, executed on the 30th day of December, A. D., 1901, by Felix Damburat and Mary Jane Damburat, his wife, to the City of Seattle, for the North 1/2 of the N.E. 1/4, the S.E. 1/4 of the N.E. 1/4, part of Lot 1, and part of the S. W. 1/4 of the N.E. 1/4, of Section 12, Township 22, Range 8 East.
